name: Barking Shibas
description:
How To Play:
  • Left Click or A to make white shiba bark
  • Right Click or D to make black shiba bark
  • Space Bar to turn around the white shiba

This game is made by Racso. All assets in the game are made by Racso, except for the dog barking sound, which is found on the internet, and has been modified.

Play my other games as well.
